comment: /**  * Set a default Locale that this resolver will return if no other locale found.  */
code: /**  * Set a default Locale that this resolver will return if no other locale found.  */ public void setDefaultLocale(@Nullable Locale defaultLocale) {     this.defaultLocale = defaultLocale. }

comment: /**  * Return the default Locale that this resolver is supposed to fall back to, if any.  */
code: /**  * Return the default Locale that this resolver is supposed to fall back to, if any.  */ @Nullable protected Locale getDefaultLocale() {     return this.defaultLocale. }
